text: Mittelsinn is a community in Main-Spessart in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Burgsinn. == Geography == === Location === Mittelsinn is in the Würzburg Region. The community has the following Gemarkungen (traditional rural cadastral areas): Mittelsinn, Forst Aura. == References == == Other websites == * Mittelsinn in the Administrative Community’s Web pages Category:Main-Spessart
title: Mittelsinn
